---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const updated = "February 2026";
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service - Toby on Fitness Tech"
  description="Terms of Service for TobyOnFitnessTech.com — the rules governing use of our fitness tech reviews, videos, and content."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <div class="mb-12 pb-8 border-b border-neutral-800">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-neutral-300">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About This Site</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          TobyOnFitnessTech ("the site," "we," "us") is a personal blog dedicated to independent reviews and commentary on fitness technology, training methodology, and related topics. By accessing or using this site, you agree to these Terms of Service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Content and Opinions</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          All content on this site — including video reviews, blog posts, and commentary — represents the personal opinions and experiences of the author. Content is provided for informational and entertainment purposes only.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Nothing on this site constitutes medical, nutritional, or professional fitness advice. Consult a qualified professional before making changes to your exercise or diet regimen.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">No Warranties</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          This site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied. We make no representations about the accuracy, completeness, or suitability of any content. We are not liable for any damages arising from your use of this site or reliance on its content.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          This site contains affiliate links. If you click a link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. See our <a href="/affiliate" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for full details. Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial opinions — products are reviewed independently.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          All original content on this site (written text, video content, graphics) is owned by Toby Glenn Peters unless otherwise noted. You may share links to content on this site but may not reproduce full articles or videos without permission.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Third-party product names, trademarks, and logos referenced in reviews belong to their respective owners. Their inclusion does not imply endorsement.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">External Links</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          This site links to external websites including YouTube, manufacturer sites, and retailers. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those sites.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          Questions? Email <a href="mailto:contact@toby.tech" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">contact@toby.tech</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
